{"tid":632300,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友工作","createTime":"2018-04-17T09:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T08:18:25.000Z","uid":145288,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"482f224d881a87b435c558e8ac36b5883ff1bbc6","tid":632300,"uid":145288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:11:03.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟有一個好fd嘅中同<br />\n當年考dse 果陣夠分入左公大<br />\n之後發現狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就無讀書成年<br />\n又無翻兼職果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n浪費左成年之後呢就報左做後門狗打算入翻啲正常大學<br />\n點知佢讀左幾個月就話覺得on9所以無讀<br />\n又浪費左一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知道佢屋企人無家底住公屋<br />\n但佢依家日日做廢青同個自私私樓仔日打夜打<br />\n小弟覺得做朋友應該要同佢講要搵工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢好似放棄人生咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想各位巴打比d指路明燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我喺咪要放棄佢了"},{"pid":"40153f5a7671f118334a679dc1820f742cc05c9b","tid":632300,"uid":143949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:12:50.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊做廢青 hehehe"},{"pid":"c2dff1ba5b3103a20db909c37ee0457757556fb3","tid":632300,"uid":145288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40153f5a7671f118334a679dc1820f742cc05c9b","tid":632300,"uid":143949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:12:50.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊做廢青 hehehe"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 手停口停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除左誠哥邊個唔想做廢青呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72dd6186e4e8a8db0cc3254b1210060178d69bbd","tid":632300,"uid":145288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"